---
Source:
  - Title: The Collected Songs of Cold Mountain
    Publisher: Copper Canyon Press
    Translator: Red Pine
    ISBN: 1556591403
    Page: 255
Author: Han Shan
---
Among high cliffs
there's plenty of breeze
no need for a fan
the cool air comes through
lit by the moon
surrounded by clouds
I sit alone
a white-haired old man
